Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.77,0:00:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天小伊請假呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  羞鳥遊你最近都沒照顧小伊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.47,0:00:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照顧山田已經讓我夠嗆了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.58,0:00:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊波小姐好像最近都沒揍其他男人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.45,0:00:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺應該沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.71,0:00:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可難說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.26,0:00:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相馬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.49,0:00:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不都說學習休息一天的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.14,0:00:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找回狀態需要三天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.14,0:00:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是太放縱她的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.30,0:00:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會比之前更狂暴的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.81,0:01:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是好好照顧她比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.52,0:01:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是擔心自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.84,0:01:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.62,0:01:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.49,0:01:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小伊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.21,0:01:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  今天沒有排你的班哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.63,0:01:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.09,0:01:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對穿女裝…有興趣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.60,0:01:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回家去
