Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.86,0:03:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想幹什麼  伊波小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.57,0:03:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在白色情人節收到了小鳥遊的回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:26.71,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}第9道菜\N小鳥登場！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.33,0:03:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.33,0:03:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.78,0:03:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被爸爸知道我收到男生的禮物了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是由於媽媽說了的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.87,0:03:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…很麻煩的事情嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.34,0:03:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前很受爸爸的溺愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.04,0:03:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說過不希望我嫁人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都不許我和男生扯上關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.15,0:03:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  為什麼不可以跟男生玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:04:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人都是狼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.85,0:04:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真晝馬上就會被襲擊  然後給吃掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人是狼  被襲擊然後給吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.10,0:04:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…爸爸也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.96,0:04:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…想把我養大後吃掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  真…真晝  冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.61,0:04:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很信任爸爸才讓爸爸養大的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.53,0:04:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.34,0:04:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.45,0:04:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被吃之前…一定要幹掉你！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.64,0:04:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打的第一個人是爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後  揍男人就成了我的壞毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.94,0:04:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來小伊的男人恐懼症的原因是父親啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.72,0:04:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～宗太好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.05,0:05:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐們不怎麼穿這樣的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這衣服最適合宗太了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊波小姐因為笨蛋父親受了許多苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伊的爸爸的確有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.15,0:05:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被知道真的是收到了男生的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎真的會引起大騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.99,0:05:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…迫不得已…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  媽媽  你搞錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的白色情人節
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女性朋友之間也會交換禮物啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的  小鳥遊是女生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊波小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.95,0:05:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…現在雖然一個人在外地工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天公司休息  我想他絕對會來確認的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.23,0:05:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是小鳥遊是男人這點暴露的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就會讓我辭職
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.37,0:06:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了  小鳥遊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.14,0:06:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了瞞過爸爸  請穿女裝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.44,0:06:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.71,0:06:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強勢的拒絕…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想辭職  在這邊工作很快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了大家  現在已經可以和男人說點話了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了  他本來就對女裝有心理陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我太勉強你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伊  好可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.76,0:06:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  是我的錯嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  情況基本聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們三個都是從哪冒出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相馬啊  伊波不做了對你來說不是很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.82,0:07:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失禮啊  我的確是不擅長面對她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為父親的任性  不得已要辭職  果然是太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在除了讓小鳥遊穿女裝  沒別的辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種…這種有趣的事  我怎能不管
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到一半…變成真心話了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次事件的根本原因
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是小鳥遊先生送回禮的關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.08,0:07:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羞鳥遊沒有錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想辭職
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是別的店的話  估計不會收留她的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我穿…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羞鳥遊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.53,0:08:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是等等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  決心動搖了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經到了這地步就認命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊  呃…就算要穿…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生制服的尺碼什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.75,0:08:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田進來的時候  看到制服有各種尺碼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假髮什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.49,0:08:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他各種…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化妝道具什麼的  用於變裝使用的  我全部都有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你真行啊  山田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田  第一次被小鳥遊先生稱讚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.28,0:08:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如乾脆…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.86,0:08:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把爸爸做掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.11,0:08:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊波小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.94,0:09:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起  小鳥遊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.86,0:09:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊  那個…總會有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像已經有辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…小…小鳥遊…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下不為例哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:44.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20\fad(500,500)}假髮：山田的私有物\N化妝品：山田的私有物\N隱形眼鏡：松本的日拋型\N胸：普通的胸墊(塞的很滿)\N制服：店裡的庫存\N長絲襪：在百元店購入的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.88,0:09:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真和諧啊  八千代
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.85,0:09:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  杏子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  其他人跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:10:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  說起來的確沒看到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  大廳空出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小鳥遊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有體力的男人不要偷懶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.07,0:10:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏…杏子姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.31,0:10:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…是小鳥遊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉我就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請叫她宗子什麼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.96,0:10:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣  羞鳥遊是因為小伊才穿女裝的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許拿他的稱呼開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.90,0:10:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就叫個可愛點的  小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.25,0:10:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}「命名=小鳥」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.18,0:10:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羞鳥遊  要是不裝得更像女人一點  會被拆穿的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能突然適應…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是聲音  快發出點更可愛的聲音來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.77,0:10:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡…歡迎光臨…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥  好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:10:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平常的立場相反了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.40,0:11:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就以這個感覺去接待客人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  不要啊  好丟人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.11,0:11:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式上場的時候要是露陷了會很麻煩的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.26,0:11:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練習練習
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真晝和父親撒謊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了隱瞞過去要小鳥遊穿女裝？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.66,0:11:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  轟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忍著  笑出來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.19,0:11:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.32,0:11:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得讓其他女生扮成小鳥遊  那樣不就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.40,0:11:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轟  男人有不得不做的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.35,0:11:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤  現在才發現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  有引起別人懷疑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人說「你好可愛啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:51.48,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（起雞皮疙瘩）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.62,0:11:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.30,0:11:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經受夠了  我不想做了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以怯場哦  小鳥遊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.27,0:12:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該可以成為完美的女角色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是成了我會困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為了讓你有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.40,0:12:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你小時候的照片給大家看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試試會不會露餡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.28,0:12:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會加油的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.43,0:12:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了隱瞞女裝的過去而穿女裝…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.14,0:12:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生就是這樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.31,0:12:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  真希望他快點來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.15,0:12:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.97,0:12:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.10,0:12:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為已經10多年沒見過他了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  也沒有興趣見他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個不孝女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是搞錯的話  對不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我來  先和你自己的父親道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就給您端水過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這裡有叫小鳥遊的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然這個人就是伊波小姐的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.27,0:13:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.99,0:13:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是個女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不出來他是個反應強烈的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不穿女裝的話  也可以混過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也太好了  穿了女裝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:13:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人要來獵殺什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面  我是伊波真晝的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女兒平時受你照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.23,0:14:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面  我叫小鳥遊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉  嚇到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.19,0:14:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  這是假槍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.39,0:14:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是用這個打人的話也很痛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.10,0:14:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是爸爸啊  他沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.82,0:14:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.23,0:14:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在說什麼  完全聽不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.95,0:14:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若無其事地去路過一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田也想到會有這樣的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在小鳥遊先生的制服裡裝了麥克風
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽的到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子…到底是何方神聖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.51,0:14:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:14:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我女兒還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  因為一人在外工作基本回不來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.31,0:15:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到了也馬上就會被揍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒好好看到過她本人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是獨生女  所以覺得她好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.80,0:15:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真晝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.63,0:15:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女兒本人卻連父親的臉都記不住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你長得好高呢  小鳥遊小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…你實際上是男人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿著女裝？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…明明是假槍  為什麼要把槍口朝著我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說失禮的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.99,0:15:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊小姐是女人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.95,0:15:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真晝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:47.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（剛剛在偷聽）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.29,0:15:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現的時機真好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從媽媽那聽說今天真晝沒有打工的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.13,0:15:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼樣都好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:16:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且算是來幫我打圓場的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊波小姐  今天是來玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,0:16:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們關係很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.02,0:16:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要發出慘叫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會露陷的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真晝  好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.48,0:16:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  他完全沒有在聽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢  我家的女兒不會和男人靠得這麼近的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.23,0:16:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是男人真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是男人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.09,0:16:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會這樣  像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.32,0:16:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帳單就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.45,0:16:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  啊…運氣真好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…請不要給客人添麻煩！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.87,0:16:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你不要偷跑來女兒打工的地方啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.96,0:16:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和誰在一起做什麼是我的自由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.14,0:16:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你管
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.27,0:16:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真晝…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.44,0:16:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還和以前一樣完全沒變  討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.81,0:17:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊小姐  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話我會揍人的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.41,0:17:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生氣起來的女兒也好萌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.42,0:17:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  好久沒有在近距離看自己的孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.49,0:17:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  正如預料的一樣  是個笨蛋父親
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  總感覺兩個人是半斤八兩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.09,0:17:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細想想  幼年時只因為被教育說「男人是狼」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.18,0:17:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就變得討厭男人的伊波小姐也有問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.03,0:17:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊波小姐  好像因為小時候父親的一句話就變得討厭男人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.52,0:17:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈  你也知道這事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:17:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.13,0:18:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢  不只是這樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.53,0:18:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說不只是這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一句話  不會讓她那麼不擅長面對男人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是數十年的累積
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓她一見到男人就會討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為禮物的書和DVD  基本都是男人為反派的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.27,0:18:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然鐵棒惡鬼是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.81,0:18:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後夏日怪談的幽靈也是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廁所的花子硬改成花子少年讀給她聽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.89,0:18:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且為了讓她擁有可以揍男人的腕力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.41,0:18:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她的攜帶物裡偷偷地放進了重物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說在攜帶物裡放了重物…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…有放進去嗎  真晝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒這回事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.32,0:18:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這書包是爸爸給我的  但很輕的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是鐵板吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.01,0:18:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.95,0:18:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是慢慢加重的  才沒讓你發現
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.10,0:19:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣…好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.67,0:19:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我絕對不會讓男人接近真晝的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一輩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.30,0:19:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.78,0:19:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.41,0:19:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個大白癡父親
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大白癡父親  大白癡父親
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.42,0:19:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為你這種奇怪的撫養方式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓伊波小姐吃了多少苦你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.76,0:19:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傾注愛是沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.77,0:19:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但孩子可不是父母的所有物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我好好考慮下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這女孩好有男子氣概啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.75,0:20:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你所說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.56,0:20:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要對我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你女兒道歉去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到了會被揍的話  寫信也好  電話也好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.72,0:20:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都要向她謝罪!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白的話馬上去執行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.97,0:20:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就先回家去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了真晝穿了女裝  還對父親說教
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.03,0:20:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊  小鳥遊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對小鳥遊先生有點刮目相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.74,0:20:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羞鳥遊是個好孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.16,0:20:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  小伊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.12,0:20:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.75,0:20:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這是完全…淪陷了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.96,0:21:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢…情不自禁地就說教起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為做了很蠢的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.28,0:21:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許給伊波小姐的父親留下了很差的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.54,0:21:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.91,0:21:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…總覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.09,0:21:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣…都無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.11,0:21:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.51,0:21:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.08,0:21:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有生氣  沒有生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…

Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.70,0:22:07.88,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}とっておき笑顔で　出会いに出かけたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.70,0:22:07.88,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}帶著精心準備的笑顏　想去外出邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.01,0:22:15.31,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}実らない響きを　初めて伝えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.01,0:22:15.31,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}心中迴響著無果的思念　第一次想要去傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.45,0:22:21.52,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}扉を開けたら　どんな恋になる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.45,0:22:21.52,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}打開這扇門的話　會成為怎樣的戀情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.73,0:22:32.39,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}今日もぐっとすっと打ったら　少し違う自分が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.73,0:22:32.39,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}今天也使勁兒痛快地揍下去後　發現有點不同的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.65,0:22:39.93,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}晴れたら宇宙も　見通せるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.65,0:22:39.93,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}天氣放晴了　是否連宇宙也能望穿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.10,0:22:44.60,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}迷ってる子猫たちもにゃを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.10,0:22:44.60,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}迷路的小貓們也喵喵叫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.78,0:22:48.25,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}みんな連れて行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.78,0:22:48.25,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}帶上大家一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.36,0:22:54.76,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}遠くの山も　手に取るように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.36,0:22:54.76,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}遠處的山巒　彷彿也能握在手裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.90,0:22:59.40,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}君となら　選んで行ける道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.90,0:22:59.40,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}與你一同　選擇可以前行的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.49,0:23:05.16,EDJ2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}映し出す　ゴールデン{\rEDC2}·{\r}ディ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.49,0:23:05.16,EDC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}映照出　Golden  Day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.00,0:23:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.73,0:23:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥兒醬太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.45,0:23:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我迷上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.51,0:23:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.90,0:23:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你自己打扮成這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.41,0:23:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.29,0:23:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是相馬為我準備服裝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.63,0:23:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後山田幫我塗脂抹粉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.81,0:23:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.10,0:23:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,則給了我胃藥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.16,0:23:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真體貼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.86,0:23:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼對我就百般戲弄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.41,0:23:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集預告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.60,0:23:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.30,0:23:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工好玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.31,0:23:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.37,0:23:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很累  但是和小小的前輩在一起工作還是很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.10,0:24:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…吶  伊波小姐是個什麼樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.83,0:24:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊波小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.58,0:24:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.14,0:24:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「疑惑的真相…、小薺打工」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.34,0:24:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  伊波小姐是？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.61,0:24:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要問這個
